NAME
    Sah::Schemas::ISBN - Various Sah schemas related to ISBN (International
    Standard Book Number)

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.008 of Sah::Schemas::ISBN (from Perl
    distribution Sah-Schemas-ISBN), released on 2020-05-27.

SAH SCHEMAS
    *   isbn

        ISBN 10 or ISBN 13 number.

        Nondigits [^0-9Xx] will be removed during coercion.

        Checksum digit must be valid.

    *   isbn10

        ISBN 10 number.

        Nondigits [^0-9Xx] will be removed during coercion.

        "x" will be converted to uppercase.

        Checksum digit must be valid.

    *   isbn13

        ISBN 13 number.

        Nondigits [^0-9] will be removed during coercion.

        Checksum digit must be valid.

        Basically EAN-13, except with additional coercion rule to coerce it
        from ISBN 10.

